function sS() {
    const {isAuthenticated: e, user: t} = dt()
      , {toast: r} = he()
      , a = ct()
      , [s,n] = g.useState(Tm[0])
      , [o,l] = g.useState(null);
    g.useState(new Set);
    const {data: c} = useQuery({
        queryKey: ["/api/subscription"],
        enabled: e
    })
      , d = (c == null ? void 0 : c.plan) === "sselfie-studio" || (t == null ? void 0 : t.plan) === "admin"
      , u = g.useCallback(async (p, h) => {
        try {
            if (!(await fetch("/api/save-selected-images", {
                method: "POST",
                headers: {
                    "Content-Type": "application/json"
                },
                body: JSON.stringify({
                    imageUrls: [p],
                    prompt: `Flatlay: ${h}`
                })
            })).ok)
                throw new Error("Failed to save image");
            a.invalidateQueries({
                queryKey: ["/api/ai-images"]
            }),
            r({
                title: "Flatlay Saved",
                description: "Added to your gallery successfully"
            })
        } catch (f) {
            console.error("Error saving flatlay:", f),
            r({
                title: "Save Failed",
                description: "Could not save flatlay to gallery",
                variant: "destructive"
            })
        }
    }
    , [a, r]);
    return e ? d ? i.jsxs("div", {
        className: "min-h-screen bg-white",
        children: [i.jsx(ye, {}), i.jsx(_a, {
            title: "Flatlay Library",
            subtitle: "Professional styled flatlays to elevate your brand",
            backgroundImage: D.flatlays.workspace1,
            textPosition: "center"
        }), i.jsxs("div", {
            className: "max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12",
            children: [i.jsxs("div", {
                className: "text-center mb-12",
                children: [i.jsx("h2", {
                    className: "text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-serif font-light text-black mb-6",
                    children: "Curated Collections"
                }), i.jsx("p", {
                    className: "text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed",
                    children: "Professional flatlay photography collections designed to complement your AI portraits. Each collection captures a distinct aesthetic to match your brand vision."
                })]
            }), i.jsx("div", {
                className: "grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12",
                children: Tm.map(p => i.jsxs("div", {
                    onClick: () => n(p),
                    className: `cursor-pointer group transition-all duration-300 ${s.id === p.id ? "ring-2 ring-black" : "hover:ring-1 hover:ring-gray-300"}`,
                    children: [i.jsx("div", {
                        className: "aspect-square bg-gray-100 overflow-hidden",
                        children: i.jsx("img", {
                            src: p.backgroundImage,
                            alt: p.name,
                            className: "w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-105"
                        })
                    }), i.jsxs("div", {
                        className: "p-6 bg-white",
                        children: [i.jsx("h3", {
                            className: "font-serif text-xl text-black mb-2",
                            children: p.name
                        }), i.jsx("p", {
                            className: "text-sm text-gray-600 mb-3",
                            children: p.description
                        }), i.jsx("p", {
                            className: "text-xs text-gray-500 italic",
                            children: p.aesthetic
                        })]
                    })]
                }, p.id))
            }), i.jsxs("div", {
                className: "mb-12",
                children: [i.jsxs("div", {
                    className: "text-center mb-8",
                    children: [i.jsx("h3", {
                        className: "text-2xl font-serif font-light text-black mb-3",
                        children: s.name
                    }), i.jsx("p", {
                        className: "text-gray-600",
                        children: s.description
                    })]
                }), i.jsx("div", {
                    className: "grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-4 xl:grid-cols-5 gap-4",
                    children: s.images.map(p => i.jsxs("div", {
                        className: "group relative aspect-square bg-gray-100 overflow-hidden cursor-pointer",
                        onClick: () => l(p.url),
                        children: [i.jsx("img", {
                            src: p.url,
                            alt: p.title,
                            className: "w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-105"
                        }), i.jsx("div", {
                            className: "absolute inset-0 bg-black bg-opacity-0 group-hover:bg-opacity-50 transition-all duration-300 flex items-end p-4",
                            children: i.jsx("div", {
                                className: "opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300",
                                children: i.jsx("button", {
                                    onClick: h => {
                                        h.stopPropagation(),
                                        u(p.url, p.title)
                                    }
                                    ,
                                    className: "bg-white text-black px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors",
                                    children: "Save to Gallery"
                                })
                            })
                        })]
                    }, p.id))
                })]
            }), i.jsx("div", {
                className: "text-center py-8 border-t border-gray-100",
                children: i.jsxs("p", {
                    className: "text-sm text-gray-500",
                    children: [s.images.length, " professional flatlays in ", s.name, " collection"]
                })
            })]
        }), o && i.jsx("div", {
            className: "fixed inset-0 bg-black bg-opacity-90 flex items-center justify-center z-50 p-4",
            onClick: () => l(null),
            children: i.jsxs("div", {
                className: "relative max-w-4xl max-h-full",
                children: [i.jsx("img", {
                    src: o,
                    alt: "Full size flatlay",
                    className: "max-w-full max-h-full object-contain",
                    onClick: p => p.stopPropagation()
                }), i.jsx("button", {
                    onClick: () => l(null),
                    className: "absolute top-4 right-4 bg-black text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors",
                    children: "×"
                })]
            })
        })]
    }) : i.jsxs("div", {
        className: "min-h-screen bg-white",
        children: [i.jsx(ye, {}), i.jsx("div", {
            className: "min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center px-4",
            children: i.jsxs("div", {
                className: "text-center max-w-md",
                children: [i.jsxs("div", {
                    className: "mb-8",
                    children: [i.jsx("div", {
                        className: "w-16 h-16 bg-gray-100 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center",
                        children: i.jsx("span", {
                            className: "text-2xl",
                            children: "🔒"
                        })
                    }), i.jsx("h1", {
                        className: "text-2xl font-serif text-black mb-4",
                        children: "Premium Feature"
                    }), i.jsx("p", {
                        className: "text-gray-600 mb-6",

    })
}

function hy(e, t) {

        if (e[0] === e[1] || t[0] === t[1])
            return t[0];
        const a = (t[1] - t[0]) / (e[1] - e[0]);
        return t[0] + a * (r - e[0])
    }
}

function IS({isOpen: e, onClose: t, liveUrl: r, brandName: a}) {
    if (!e)
        return null;
    const s = () => {
        navigator.clipboard.writeText(r);
        const n = document.getElementById("copy-url-btn");
        if (n) {
            const o = n.textContent;
            n.textContent = "Copied",
            setTimeout( () => {
                n.textContent = o
            }
            , 1500)
        }
    }
    ;
    return i.jsx("div", {
        className: "fixed inset-0 bg-black/60 backdrop-blur-sm z-50 flex items-center justify-center p-4",
        children: i.jsxs("div", {
            className: "bg-white w-full max-w-md mx-4 rounded-none shadow-2xl",
            children: [i.jsxs("div", {
                className: "text-center p-8 border-b border-gray-100",
                children: [i.jsx("div", {
                    className: "mb-6",
                    children: i.jsx("div", {
                        className: "w-16 h-16 mx-auto bg-black rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4",
                        children: i.jsx("span", {
                            className: "text-white text-2xl",
                            children: "✓"
                        })
                    })
                }), i.jsx("h2", {
                    className: "text-2xl mb-2 text-black font-light tracking-wide",
                    style: {
                        fontFamily: "'Times New Roman', serif"
                    },
                    children: "Your Brand Is Live"
                }), i.jsxs("p", {
                    className: "text-gray-600 text-sm tracking-wide uppercase",
                    style: {
                        letterSpacing: "0.1em"
                    },
                    children: [a, " • Published Successfully"]
                })]
            }), i.jsxs("div", {
                className: "p-8",
                children: [i.jsxs("div", {
                    className: "text-center mb-8",
                    children: [i.jsx("p", {

                        children: "Your professional landing page is now live and ready for your audience."

                                letterSpacing: "0.1em"
                            },
                            children: "Live URL"
                        }), i.jsx("p", {
                            className: "text-sm font-mono text-black break-all",

                        })]
                    }), i.jsxs("div", {

function MS() {
    const [e,t] = g.useState(!0)
      , [r,a] = g.useState(!1)
      , [s,n] = g.useState("")
      , [o,l] = g.useState("home")
      , c = g.useRef(null)
      , {data: d} = ae({

                    className: "text-2xl font-light text-black mb-6",
                    children: "Choose Flatlay Style"
                }), i.jsx("div", {
                    className: "grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6",
                    children: (h = l == null ? void 0 : l.flatlayCollections) == null ? void 0 : h.map(f => i.jsx("div", {
                        className: `cursor-pointer transition-all duration-200 ${s === f.name ? "ring-4 ring-black ring-offset-2" : "hover:ring-2 hover:ring-gray-300 hover:ring-offset-2"}`,
                        onClick: () => n(f.name),
                        children: i.jsxs("div", {
                            className: "bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4",
                            children: [i.jsx("h3", {
                                className: "text-lg font-light text-black mb-3",
                                children: f.name
                            }), i.jsx("div", {
                                className: "grid grid-cols-3 gap-2",
                                children: f.images.slice(0, 3).map( (y, x) => i.jsx("div", {
                                    className: "aspect-square bg-gray-100 rounded overflow-hidden",
                                    children: i.jsx("img", {
                                        src: y,
                                        alt: `${f.name} ${x + 1}`,
                                        className: "w-full h-full object-cover",
                                        loading: "lazy"
                                    })
                                }, x))
                            }), s === f.name && i.jsx("div", {
                                className: "mt-3 text-center",
                                children: i.jsx("span", {
                                    className: "text-sm text-black",
                                    children: "Selected ✓"
                                })
                            })]
                        })
                    }, f.name))
                })]
            }), i.jsxs("div", {
                className: "flex items-center justify-between border-t border-gray-200 pt-8",
                children: [i.jsx(G, {
                    href: "/workspace",
                    className: "text-gray-600 hover:text-black transition-colors",
                    children: "← Back to Workspace"
                }), i.jsx("button", {
                    onClick: p,
                    disabled: r.length === 0 || d.isPending,
                    className: "bg-black text-white px-8 py-3 rounded hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed",
                    children: d.isPending ? "Saving..." : "Continue to Brand Story"
                })]
            })]
        })]
    })
}

        businessName: "",

        email: "",
        location: "",

      , {toast: o} = he();

        queryKey: ["/api/brand-onboarding"],
        retry: !1
    });
    g.useEffect( () => {
        l && !c && n({
            businessName: l.businessName || "",

function FS() {
    const {user: e, isAuthenticated: t, isLoading: r} = dt()
      , [,a] = ve()
      , {toast: s} = he()
      , [n,o] = g.useState(!1);
    return g.useEffect( () => {
        t && !r && !n && (async () => {
            if (!(!t || !e || n)) {
                o(!0);
                try {
                    const d = localStorage.getItem("userPlan") || localStorage.getItem("selectedPlan") || "free";
                    console.log("Setting up user account with plan:", d);
                    const u = await pe("POST", "/api/setup-plan", {
                        plan: d
                    });
                    if (u.ok) {
                        const p = await u.json();
                        console.log("Plan setup successful:", p),
                        localStorage.removeItem("userPlan"),
                        localStorage.removeItem("selectedPlan"),
                        s({
                            title: "Welcome to SSELFIE Studio!",
                            description: "Your account has been set up successfully."
                        }),
                        setTimeout( () => {
                            a("/workspace")
                        }
                        , 1e3)
                    } else
                        throw new Error("Failed to setup plan")
                } catch (c) {
                    console.error("Plan setup error:", c),
                    s({
                        title: "Setup Error",
                        description: "There was an issue setting up your account. Please try again.",
                        variant: "destructive"
                    }),
                    setTimeout( () => {
                        a("/workspace")
                    }
                    , 2e3)
                }
            }
        }

                },
